abstract: The latest home price index showed a small gain in October, but prices, seasonally adjusted, are coming down again in some of the worst hit markets.
snippet: The latest home price index showed a small gain in October, but prices, seasonally adjusted, are coming down again in some of the worst hit markets.
lead_paragraph: The S.&P. Case-Shiller numbers out today, for October, show another small gain in home prices for the national composite.
